      <abstract label="Abstract">The Trio Beauty Salon Collection, 1935-2007, consists of four
        Hollinger boxes containing various records and mementos related to the Trio Beauty Salon of
        Harrisonburg, VA including legal and financial documents, record books, and personal
        documents of the operators of the salon. </abstract>
      <origination label="Creator" encodinganalog="100$a">Flora Evelyn Taylor, Mildred Bridges, Ava
        Gowl, Ruby Dove, Beulah Ruth Kerns</origination>
    </did>
